rows.label: qst200916_0010
rows.name: She kome bak!

rows.label: qst200916_0020
rows.name: Kalamity witch return!

rows.label: qst200916_0030
rows.name: Hello, people of the Tirkin tribe!

rows.label: qst200916_0040
rows.name: H-hello...

rows.label: qst200916_0050
rows.name: *cheep* Hello...

rows.label: qst200916_0060
rows.name: They seem surprisingly timid for whatever reason...

rows.label: qst200916_0070
rows.name:
Hmm. I bet we'll be able to negotiate with them
this time round... Just leave it to me.

rows.label: qst200916_0080
rows.name:
I'd like you to hand over the cargo you stole from
the Nopon merchant Kupon, if you please.

rows.label: qst200916_0090
rows.name: We have thing like that?

rows.label: qst200916_0100
rows.name: You one who took, no?

rows.label: qst200916_0110
rows.name:
Just give us the cargo and
we'll leave quietly.

rows.label: qst200916_0120
rows.name: Maybe we give bak?

rows.label: qst200916_0130
rows.name: Yah, give bak, or get zap zap again...

rows.label: qst200916_0140
rows.name:
Relax. We didn't come here to pick a fight.
So...please?

rows.label: qst200916_0150
rows.name: She being nice to us...

rows.label: qst200916_0160
rows.name: What do? We be nice bak?

rows.label: qst200916_0170
rows.name: Skraaawk! Me no want no zap zap!

rows.label: qst200916_0180
rows.name: No! We not anger kalamity witch!

rows.label: qst200916_0190
rows.name: Quick! Give bak! Give!

rows.label: qst200916_0200
rows.name:
Huh? Another storm's coming?
What a coincidence.

rows.label: qst200916_0210
rows.name: No bring zap zap!

rows.label: qst200916_0220
rows.name: We not give kargo!

rows.label: qst200916_0230
rows.name: Not give! Not give!

rows.label: qst200916_0240
rows.name: *sigh* It would appear that's the negotiations over.

rows.label: qst200916_0250
rows.name: Well, guess we'll just have to give 'em a whupping!
